				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Bard Top 10 Issue Search, Take 2, Voting<a name="74661"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 20 05 11:03 AM</span></td>
